            "id": 6009987,
            "title": "國航7月推軍人國際線優先登機 交長：未來考量納入軍眷",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>政府為表達對國軍長期守護國家安全的感謝，宣布包括華航 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2610:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2610\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2610-TW</a>) 等 6 家國籍航空公司國際線航班，將同步推出「軍人優先登機服務」。交通部長陳世凱今 (6) 日表示，此一對於軍人感謝的尊榮服務，將於 7 月 1 日起實施，預估未來第 2 階段評估是否納入軍人眷屬。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009987%2Fl%2F2a189ae852eafdc5ca9bee8121d0df9f.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">國航7月推軍人國際線優先登機，交長：未來考量納入軍眷。(圖:民航局提供)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>交通部民航局表示，7 月 1 日起，國籍航空於航班進行登機作業時，將透過登機廣播邀請軍人優先登機；現役軍人若本人出示軍人身份證供識別後，在我國機場搭乘華航、長榮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2618:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2618\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2618-TW</a>)、星宇 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2646:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2646\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2646-TW</a>)、台虎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:6757:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6757\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6757-TW</a>)、華信及立榮等 6 家國航的國際線航班，將可享有優先登機禮遇。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>陳世凱今天與國防部長顧立雄連袂出席記者會，包括代表國籍航空業者致詞的華航董事長高星潢，均肯定國軍長年以來為守護國家安全所做的貢獻。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>陳世凱說，國航提供軍人優先登機服務，象徵對軍人長期守護國家的尊崇與肯定，國軍無私奉獻在第一線守護國家，國家才能安定、人民才能安心，未來交通部也將持續與各界攜手合作，推動更多有意義的服務措施。目前交通部門將提供給現役軍人尊榮登機禮遇和優先，盼趕在暑假 7 月 1 日就讓所有軍人享受尊榮禮遇。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>陳世凱也表示，未來第 2 階段希望擴大服務，努力讓現役軍人眷屬也能享優先登機尊榮，可直接走商務通道報到。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>顧立雄則感謝業者提供服務，強調此看似平凡的安排，卻也對軍人恪守職責的肯定與感謝，提升了軍人地位，讓他們為國貢獻的價值獲得最好的詮釋。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
